Summary: This section provides the inheritance details and a brief description of the Control class, the base class for all GUI elements in Godot.

Inherits: CanvasItem < Node < Object

Inherited By: BaseButton, ColorRect, Container, GraphEdit, ItemList, Label, LineEdit, MenuBar, NinePatchRect, Panel, Range, ReferenceRect, RichTextLabel, Separator, TabBar, TextEdit, TextureRect, Tree, VideoStreamPlayer, VirtualJoystick

Control is the base class for all GUI controls. It adapts its position and size based on its parent control.
