Summary: A list of the Control node's properties, covering accessibility, layout, focus, mouse handling, theming, and tooltips.

* accessibility_controls_nodes (Array[NodePath]): A list of NodePaths to other controls that are controlled by this one. Default: `[]`.
* accessibility_described_by_nodes (Array[NodePath]): A list of NodePaths to other controls that describe this one. Default: `[]`.
* accessibility_description (String): A textual description of the control's purpose for accessibility tools. Default: `""`.
* accessibility_flow_to_nodes (Array[NodePath]): A list of NodePaths to other controls that should be read after this one by screen readers. Default: `[]`.
* accessibility_labeled_by_nodes (Array[NodePath]): A list of NodePaths to other controls that label this one. Default: `[]`.
* accessibility_live (AccessibilityLiveMode): Specifies how screen readers should handle changes to this control. Default: `0`.
* accessibility_name (String): The name of the control for accessibility tools. Default: `""`.
* anchor_bottom (float): The vertical anchor point for the bottom edge of the control, relative to its parent. Default: `0.0`.
* anchor_left (float): The horizontal anchor point for the left edge of the control, relative to its parent. Default: `0.0`.
* anchor_right (float): The horizontal anchor point for the right edge of the control, relative to its parent. Default: `0.0`.
* anchor_top (float): The vertical anchor point for the top edge of the control, relative to its parent. Default: `0.0`.
* auto_translate (bool): When enabled, the control's text is automatically translated using the project's translation settings.
* clip_contents (bool): If true, any child nodes that exceed the control's bounding rectangle will be clipped. Default: `false`.
* custom_minimum_size (Vector2): The minimum size of the control. If set to a value greater than (0, 0), it will always be at least this size. Default: `Vector2(0, 0)`.
* focus_behavior_recursive (FocusBehaviorRecursive): Determines how focus is handled for this control and its children. Default: `0`.
* focus_mode (FocusMode): Defines how the control can be focused. Default: `0`.
* focus_neighbor_bottom (NodePath): The NodePath to the control that should receive focus when the down arrow key is pressed. Default: `NodePath("")`.
* focus_neighbor_left (NodePath): The NodePath to the control that should receive focus when the left arrow key is pressed. Default: `NodePath("")`.
* focus_neighbor_right (NodePath): The NodePath to the control that should receive focus when the right arrow key is pressed. Default: `NodePath("")`.
* focus_neighbor_top (NodePath): The NodePath to the control that should receive focus when the up arrow key is pressed. Default: `NodePath("")`.
* focus_next (NodePath): The NodePath to the next control in the focus chain (used when Tab is pressed). Default: `NodePath("")`.
* focus_previous (NodePath): The NodePath to the previous control in the focus chain (used when Shift+Tab is pressed). Default: `NodePath("")`.
* global_position (Vector2): The control's global position, relative to the top-left corner of the viewport.
* grow_horizontal (GrowDirection): Controls how the control resizes horizontally when its parent container resizes. Default: `1`.
* grow_vertical (GrowDirection): Controls how the control resizes vertically when its parent container resizes. Default: `1`.
* layout_direction (LayoutDirection): Sets the layout direction for right-to-left language support. Default: `0`.
* localize_numeral_system (bool): If true, the numeral system used in the control will be localized based on the current locale. Default: `true`.
* mouse_behavior_recursive (MouseBehaviorRecursive): Determines how mouse events are handled for this control and its children. Default: `0`.
* mouse_default_cursor_shape (CursorShape): The default cursor shape to display when the mouse is over this control. Default: `0`.
* mouse_filter (MouseFilter): Controls how the control handles mouse events (pass, stop, or ignore). Default: `0`.
* mouse_force_pass_scroll_events (bool): If true, scroll events are always passed to the parent, even if the control has a custom mouse filter. Default: `true`.
* offset_bottom (float): The bottom margin of the control, relative to its bottom anchor. Default: `0.0`.
* offset_left (float): The left margin of the control, relative to its left anchor. Default: `0.0`.
* offset_right (float): The right margin of the control, relative to its right anchor. Default: `0.0`.
* offset_top (float): The top margin of the control, relative to its top anchor. Default: `0.0`.
* offset_transform_enabled (bool): If true, the offset transform properties are applied. Default: `false`.
* offset_transform_pivot (Vector2): The pivot point for the offset transform, in pixels. Default: `Vector2(0, 0)`.
* offset_transform_pivot_ratio (Vector2): The pivot point for the offset transform, as a ratio of the control's size. Default: `Vector2(0.5, 0.5)`.
* offset_transform_position (Vector2): The position offset applied to the control, in pixels. Default: `Vector2(0, 0)`.
* offset_transform_position_ratio (Vector2): The position offset applied to the control, as a ratio of the control's size. Default: `Vector2(0, 0)`.
* offset_transform_rotation (float): The rotation offset applied to the control, in radians. Default: `0.0`.
* offset_transform_scale (Vector2): The scale offset applied to the control. Default: `Vector2(1, 1)`.
* offset_transform_visual_only (bool): If true, the offset transform only affects the visual appearance and not the collision or input detection. Default: `true`.
* physics_interpolation_mode (PhysicsInterpolationMode): The physics interpolation mode for the control. Default: `2` (overrides Node.physics_interpolation_mode).
* pivot_offset (Vector2): The offset of the rotation and scaling pivot, in pixels. Default: `Vector2(0, 0)`.
* pivot_offset_ratio (Vector2): The offset of the rotation and scaling pivot, as a ratio of the control's size. Default: `Vector2(0, 0)`.
* position (Vector2): The control's position relative to its parent. Default: `Vector2(0, 0)`.
* rotation (float): The rotation of the control, in radians. Default: `0.0`.
* rotation_degrees (float): The rotation of the control, in degrees.
* scale (Vector2): The scale of the control. Default: `Vector2(1, 1)`.
* shortcut_context (Node): The node that provides the context for shortcuts.
* size (Vector2): The size of the control, in pixels. Default: `Vector2(0, 0)`.
* size_flags_horizontal (SizeFlags): A bitfield that controls how the control resizes horizontally within a container. Default: `1`.
* size_flags_stretch_ratio (float): The stretch ratio used when the control is in a container. Default: `1.0`.
* size_flags_vertical (SizeFlags): A bitfield that controls how the control resizes vertically within a container. Default: `1`.
* theme (Theme): The custom Theme resource for this control and its children.
* theme_type_variation (StringName): A StringName that specifies a theme type variation to use for this control. Default: `&""`.
* tooltip_auto_translate_mode (AutoTranslateMode): The auto-translation mode for the tooltip text. Default: `0`.
* tooltip_text (String): The text that appears in a tooltip when the mouse is hovered over the control. Default: `""`.
---CHUNK---
